      "text": "……やっぱり隠れて踊っていたんだな\nまぁ、葵ならやりかねないとは思っていたけど",
      "startTime": 257.6666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi022.m4a",
      "text": "僕にとって、踊ることは呼吸と一緒なんだ\nやめたら生きていけないよ",
      "startTime": 264.3333374023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
