      "text": "……分かったよ。でも、もう課題をもらったり\nしないよう気をつけてくれよ",
      "startTime": 270.1188656259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi023.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、{user}君にも\n迷惑掛けちゃったしね",
      "startTime": 274.0211897417,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi024.m4a",
      "text": "僕のせいで君の夏休みまでなくなっちゃったでしょ？\n悪かったよ",
      "startTime": 280.400004069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "俺のことはいいんだ\nそんなことより葵。今年の夏は全然遊んでないだろ？",
      "startTime": 283.6666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi025.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。夏休みの前半は仕事漬けで\n後半は宿題漬けだったからね",
      "startTime": 292.4666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi026.m4a",
      "text": "今年の夏は寂しく終わりそうだよ",
      "startTime": 295.0333394368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh021.m4a",
      "text": "（……友達と遊ぶのも、今しか出来ない貴重な経験だ）\n（一日くらい、楽しく過ごさせてあげたい）",
      "startTime": 303.100004069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh022.m4a",
      "text": "（とはいえ、今の葵には仕事の依頼が殺到している）\n（葵もきっと仕事を優先するだろう）",
      "startTime": 310.7321650423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi027.m4a",
      "text": "急に考え込んでどうしたの？",
      "startTime": 313.4666727702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh023.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　なあ、葵、次の仕事なんだけど\n――LizNoirのみんなで、夏を楽しんでみないか",
      "startTime": 320.5666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
